                <ul class="cognitive-icon-group">
                    <li>
                        <div class="cognitive-icon"><img src="//resource.cdn.azure.cn/marketing-resource/css/images/home,features,api-management-01-api.png"/></div>
                        <div class="cognitive-text">
                            <h2>Create an API gateway and developer portal in minutes</h2>
                            <p>Use Azure API Management as a turnkey solution for releasing APIs to internal and external customers. Quickly create consistent and modern API gateways for existing back-end services hosted anywhere, secure them from abuse and overuse, and get insights into their usage and health status. You can also automate and scale developer onboarding to help get your API program up and running.</p>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                    <li>
