                        <div class="cognitive-text">
                            <h2>Use any host, API, or scale</h1>
                            <p>Use an API management platform that works the way you do. Securely connect to back-end services built and running on any technology stack regardless of whether you select Azure or another service to host your APIs. API Management can be used worldwide and scaled as required. It can also handle any traffic growth or spike without service interruptions.</p>
                        </div>
                    </li>                    
